---
import RightArrow from '/public/svg/RightArrow.svg'
import Rocket from '/public/svg/Rocket.svg'
---
<section class="mb-24 mt-12 scroll-mt-40 md:scroll-mt-44" id="hero">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-6">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-brand-primary/10 border border-brand-primary/20">
      <Rocket class="text-brand-primary size-3.5"/>
      <span class="font-label select-none text-small uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-primary">Disponibilidad Inmediata</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="font-headline select-none text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tighter text-glow">
      Hola, soy Bryan
      <span class="block text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-brand-primary via-brand-secondary to-brand-tertiary">desarrollador web</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="font-body select-none text-lg text-brand-on-surface-variant max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
      Especializado en construir interfaces inmersivas y escalables. Transformando ideas complejas en experiencias digitales fluidas a través del código.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 w-full sm:w-auto mt-4">
      <a 
        href="#projects"
        aria-label="Ver mis proyectos destacados"
        class="ion-drive-button cursor-pointer px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-black active:scale-95 transition-transform"
      >
        Ver Proyectos
        <RightArrow class="text-base size-4"/>
      </a>
      <a 
        href="#contact"
        class="glass-panel cursor-pointer ghost-border px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-brand-primary font-bold font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-2 active:scale-95 transition-transform"
      >
        Contactar
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
